arts.ttl: FRANZ BECKENBAUER SUPER CUP PLAYER RATINGS | VfB Stuttgart 1-2 Bayern Munich
arts.sum: Top-flight German football returns with the Franz Beckenbauer Super Cup between VfB Stuttgart and Bayern Munich.

arts.ttl: Stuttgart chief confirms Woltemade's transfer to Bayern is off the table
arts.sum: VfB Stuttgart chairman Alexander Wehrle has made it clear that Nick Woltemade will not be moving to Bayern Munich.

arts.ttl: Almost no hope left - Woltemade's move to Bayern likely to collapse
arts.sum: After one of the longest transfer sagas in this year, Nick Woltemade's tranfer to Bayern Munich will likely collapse - only one Bayern official is still hopeful.

arts.ttl: "Very difficult, but still on" - Fabrizio Romano on Bayern's pursuit of Woltemade
arts.sum: The transfer expert believes Bayern haven't given up on the 23-year-old just yet.

arts.ttl: PREVIEW | Franz Beckenbauer Supercup: Stuttgart vs Bayern Munich
arts.sum: Reigning Bundesliga champions Bayern Munich face DFB Pokal winners Stuttgart at the MHP Arena on Saturday evening in the season’s traditional curtain-raiser, the Franz Beckenbauer Super Cup – the first…

arts.ttl: Woltemade willing to forego millions for Bayern move, Sky Germany reveal exclusive details
arts.sum: The 23-year-old and his agent are prepared to make sacrifices to join the reigning Bundesliga champions.
